description.en: Passport is a decentralized application (DApp) built on Paparazzi’s blockchain platform Vitae. Vitae, a latin word for life, is built for scalability and simplicity. Vitae is built using Tendermint blockchain framework. With a robust architecture in design, Axis Labs and Paparazzi team is building a frictionless blockchain platform customized for the Paparazzi ecosystem. Later, Vitae Network will utilize Axis Lab’s layer two technology.
